{"data":[{"date":"16:53 23/07","title":"V\u0103n To\u00e0n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t... S\u01a1n T\u00f9ng M-TP","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/van-toan-xuat-hien-voi-kieu-dau-dam-chat-son-tung-mtp.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4540","checkdouble":"191843"},{"date":"19:47 23/07","title":"Ozil chia tay tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern h\u1ea3 h\u00ea m\u1ea1t s\u00e1t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/ozil-chia-tay-tuyen-duc-chu-tich-bayern-ha-he-mat-sat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Uli Hoeness vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m th\u1eb3ng m\u1eb7t ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00ec b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i x\u00f4n xao \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u1ee1 ng\u00e0ng v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd chia tay \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng Mesut Ozil sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, v\u1edbi 23 b\u00e0n/92 tr\u1eadn c\u00f9ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-vat/tam-thu-cua-mesut-ozil-giot-nuoc-tran-ly-389-191838.html\" target=\"_blank\">Qua m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c t\u00e2m th\u01b0 d\u00e0i d\u1eb1ng d\u1eb7c</span> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean c\u00e1c trang m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n n\u1ed7i u\u1ea5t ngh\u1eb9n trong l\u00f2ng khi b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern Munich h\u1ea3 h\u00ea m\u1ea1t s\u00e1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern Munich h\u1ea3 h\u00ea m\u1ea1t s\u00e1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/ozil-chia-tay-dtqg-nguoi-duc-cang-thay-ha-he.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00ec b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal chia s\u1ebb ngu\u1ed3n c\u01a1n ch\u00ednh y\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 v\u1ee5 b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 nh\u1eadp c\u01b0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp, gh\u00e9t b\u1ecf hay g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 th\u1ecb, ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern Munich h\u1ea3 h\u00ea m\u1ea1t s\u00e1t Ozil</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u1ea7n \u0111a gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Ozil b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, trong khi d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng \u0111ang chia ng\u1ea3 v\u00ec anh, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i c\u00f3 Uli Hoeness s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ni\u1ec1m vui s\u01b0\u1edbng ra m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m, m\u1ea1t s\u00e1t nh\u00e0 c\u1ef1u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern Munich: \u201cTin tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t trong ng\u1ef3! N\u00f3i th\u1eadt th\u00ec Ozil \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 c*t trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua r\u1ed3i. L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t c\u1eadu ta tranh ch\u1ea5p tay \u0111\u00f4i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup... 2014. \u1ede tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u1eadu ta ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec1n ngang, v\u00e0 gi\u1edd th\u00ec l\u1ea5y L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ee5y bi\u1ec7n cho nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cM\u1ed7i khi Bayern Munich g\u1eb7p Arsenal, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u1eadp trung khoan ph\u00e1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Ozil b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u1edd c\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi hay sao khi ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ozil, vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i \u0111i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Reinhard Grindel, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Oliver Bierhoff hay HLV Joachim Low?\u201d</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/mesut-\u00f6zil-nan-nhan-dien-hinh-cua-mot-nuoc-duc-chia-re-vi-chinh-sach-nhap-cu-389-191848.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/mesut-zil-nan-nhan-dien-hinh-cua-mot-nuoc-duc-chia-re-vi-chinh-sach-nhap-cu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/mesut-\u00f6zil-nan-nhan-dien-hinh-cua-mot-nuoc-duc-chia-re-vi-chinh-sach-nhap-cu-389-191848.html\">Mesut \u00d6zil: N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c chia r\u1ebd v\u00ec ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp c\u01b0</span><br>\r\nSau \u00d6zil h\u00f4m nay, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai s\u1ebd c\u00f2n bao nhi\u00eau \u00d6zil n\u1eefa? V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u00f3 g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i kh\u00e1c, \u0111ang tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh trong nh\u1eefng H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c, khi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4539","checkdouble":"191852"},{"date":"23:30 23/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Arsenal \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/nguoi-arsenal-ung-ho-tien-ve-mesut-ozil-chia-tay-doi-tuyen-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Hector Bellerin l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea5p CLB v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf khi b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh L\u0110B\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Mesut Ozil b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c khi ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 29, b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 x\u1ee9ng danh c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n v\u1edbi 23 b\u00e0n/92 tr\u1eadn c\u00f9ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/mesut-ozil-cay-dang-bo-tuyen-that-bai-cua-ca-nen-bong-da.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Qua b\u1ee9c t\u00e2m th\u01b0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n n\u1ed7i u\u1ea5t ngh\u1eb9n trong l\u00f2ng khi b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Mannschaft. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n s\u00e2u xa h\u01a1n v\u1eady khi n\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n ch\u00ednh g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c nh\u1eadp c\u01b0 t\u1eeb Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp, gh\u00e9t b\u1ecf hay g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 th\u1ecb, ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Hector Bellerin s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh \u1edf c\u1ea5p CLB \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. D\u00f2ng tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean Twitter c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha: <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p sau bi\u1ebft bao nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p, c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea3 trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. Ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i ca ng\u1ee3i Mesut Ozil v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng l\u00ean b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 anh \u1ea5y v\u00ec nh\u1eefng g\u00ec d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m. Ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c m\u00e3i m\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 dung t\u00fang trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u01b0 lu\u1eadn \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 chia ng\u1ea3 v\u00ec Ozil khi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Bellerin ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Uli Hoeness c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ozil-chia-tay-tuyen-duc-chu-tich-bayern-ha-he-mat-sat-184-191852.html\" target=\"_blank\">v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1eadm t\u1ec7, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m, m\u1ea1t s\u00e1t anh</span>.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/mesut-\u00f6zil-nan-nhan-dien-hinh-cua-mot-nuoc-duc-chia-re-vi-chinh-sach-nhap-cu-389-191848.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/mesut-zil-nan-nhan-dien-hinh-cua-mot-nuoc-duc-chia-re-vi-chinh-sach-nhap-cu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/mesut-\u00f6zil-nan-nhan-dien-hinh-cua-mot-nuoc-duc-chia-re-vi-chinh-sach-nhap-cu-389-191848.html\">Mesut \u00d6zil: N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c chia r\u1ebd v\u00ec ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp c\u01b0</span><br>\r\nSau \u00d6zil h\u00f4m nay, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai s\u1ebd c\u00f2n bao nhi\u00eau \u00d6zil n\u1eefa? V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u00f3 g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i kh\u00e1c, \u0111ang tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh trong nh\u1eefng H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c, khi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4538","checkdouble":"191865"},{"date":"00:00 24/07","title":"L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o Ozil sau c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/ldbd-duc-phan-phao-ozil-sau-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Mesut Ozil, sau khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf trong n\u1ed7i u\u1ea5t h\u1eadn.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 g\u00e2y x\u00f4n xao, b\u00e0ng ho\u00e0ng d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, Mesut Ozil quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c khi ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 29, b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 x\u1ee9ng danh c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n v\u1edbi 23 b\u00e0n/92 tr\u1eadn c\u00f9ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Mannschaft. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n s\u00e2u xa h\u01a1n v\u1eady khi n\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n ch\u00ednh g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c nh\u1eadp c\u01b0 t\u1eeb Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp, gh\u00e9t b\u1ecf hay g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 th\u1ecb, ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u0110B\u0110 ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u0110B\u0110 ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/ldbd-duc-phan-phao-ozil-sau-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 b\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o v\u00ec c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o d\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ed9i dung c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft nh\u01b0 sau:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cNh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh ch\u1ee5p chung v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 Recep Tayyip Erdogan d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi lo ng\u1ea1i trong l\u00f2ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i \u0110\u1ee9c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m trong s\u1ef1 v\u1ee5 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t l\u1ea5y l\u00e0m ti\u1ebfc khi Mesut Ozil c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ea5n n\u1ea1n ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c, trong khi Jerome Boateng th\u00ec ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cL\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac n\u1ebfu Mesut Ozil v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i ri\u00eang cho m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c v\u00f4 l\u00fd v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng khai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i xin nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edc c\u1ef1c tham gia h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c nh\u1eadp c\u01b0 cho \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc trong r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/mesut-\u00f6zil-nan-nhan-dien-hinh-cua-mot-nuoc-duc-chia-re-vi-chinh-sach-nhap-cu-389-191848.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/mesut-zil-nan-nhan-dien-hinh-cua-mot-nuoc-duc-chia-re-vi-chinh-sach-nhap-cu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/mesut-\u00f6zil-nan-nhan-dien-hinh-cua-mot-nuoc-duc-chia-re-vi-chinh-sach-nhap-cu-389-191848.html\">Mesut \u00d6zil: N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c chia r\u1ebd v\u00ec ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp c\u01b0</span><br>\r\nSau \u00d6zil h\u00f4m nay, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai s\u1ebd c\u00f2n bao nhi\u00eau \u00d6zil n\u1eefa? V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u00f3 g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i kh\u00e1c, \u0111ang tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh trong nh\u1eefng H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c, khi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4537","checkdouble":"191871"},{"date":"06:16 24/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/7: B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City m\u00f9a sau","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/5/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-247-bat-ngo-voi-doi-thu-lon-nhat-cua-man-city-mua-sau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 24/7. \r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o s\u1ebd c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf m\u00f9a sau?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Leroy Sane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, khi cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho r\u1eb1ng, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn c\u00e1ch Napoli thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 xem&rdquo; &ndash; Sane cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/7 Ai l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 247 Ai l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-247-Ai-la-doi-thu-lon-nhat-cua-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24/7: Sane \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi kh\u00f3 Barca<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi CLB T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Willian b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7ng h\u1ecfi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh cho bi\u1ebft Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o d\u01b0\u1edbi&hellip; 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ecbu chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, ho\u1eb7c Barcelona s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng cho Martial<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man United \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Mourinho treo gi\u00e1. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n anh b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i Premier League. Bayern v\u00e0 Juve l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb mua s\u1eafm ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111em v\u1ec1 Pepe Reina, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u0103m nay 35 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, Reina l\u00e0 tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri t\u1ea1i Napoli, nh\u01b0ng anh m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n sang AC Milan ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. N\u1ebfu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a The Blues, c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf Milan b\u1ed7ng d\u01b0ng c\u00f3 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/7\" title=\"thu mon Pepe Reina toi Milan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/thu-mon-pepe-reina-toi-milan-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24/7: Pepe Reina m\u1edbi t\u1edbi Milan v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea h\u1ecfi mua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Karius tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 Liverpool v\u00ec mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Kop m\u1edbi k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Loris Karius. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi CLB kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, Karius c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn anh kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111ang l\u00e0m l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang hay sai, sau v\u00f4 v\u00e0n nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4536","checkdouble":"191872"},{"date":"01:47 24/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Real Madrid h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/5/24/tan-binh-real-madrid-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng 18 tu\u1ed5i Vinicius Junior t\u1ecf ra tham v\u1ecdng ngay sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 46 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Santiago de Bernabeu.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, c\u00e1i t\u00ean v\u00f4 danh Vinicius Junior b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u00e2y s\u1ed1t khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tu\u1ed5i teen \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb Kylian Mbappe ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. Theo \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 17 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1ea5y gi\u1edd, t\u1ee9c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao PSG, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Flamengo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 46 tri\u1ec7u euro.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Vinicius c\u1ee7a Real Madrid h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Vinicius c\u1ee7a Real Madrid h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/5/24/tan-binh-real-madrid-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n binh Vinicius c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 12/07/2018, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Vinicius tr\u00f2n 18 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Flamengo theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Vinicius t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i su\u1ed1t ba m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 4/5 n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t ngay khi kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh m\u00e0u \u00e1o tr\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u00f4i, c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh, b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o l\u00e2y. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecfi t\u00f4i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, t\u00f4i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t Brazil c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Bernabeu, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i m\u01b0\u1eddng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Tr\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, t\u00f4i tin m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Real Madrid v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League n\u0103m th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/neymar-moi-buong-loi-phu-phang-voi-barcelona-184-187486.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/neymar-moi-buong-loi-phu-phang-voi-barcelona.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/neymar-moi-buong-loi-phu-phang-voi-barcelona-184-187486.html\">\u201cNeymar m\u1edbi\u201d bu\u00f4ng l\u1eddi ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Barcelona</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 45 tri\u1ec7u euro \u2013 Vinicius Jr ca ng\u1ee3i Real Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, sau khi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Barca.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4535","checkdouble":"191869"},{"date":"03:12 24/07","title":"Klopp t\u1ecf l\u00f2ng \"th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea1i\" Tottenham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/klopp-to-long-thuong-hai-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u n\u1ed7i kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00e0ng th\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng cho Tottenham.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Liverpool \u0111ang tham gia v\u00e0o chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 v\u1edbi n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4n l\u00ean t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t ngay c\u1ea3 khi Premier League \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Tottenham v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea1i cho l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Tottenham v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea1i cho l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/klopp-to-long-thuong-hai-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Tottenham hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u n\u1ed7i kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, HLV Jurgen Klopp c\u00e0ng th\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng cho Tottenham, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i v\u1edbi 9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Qua \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 UEFA c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i vi\u1ec7c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf sao cho h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. HLV Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Tottenham cho bi\u1ebft:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cGi\u1edd th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 Nations League (gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0110TQG nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng cho c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i), t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 sau ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y hai th\u00e1ng sau World Cup.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eadt \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eafc nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. Tr\u00f4ng sang Tottenham v\u1edbi 9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1eed tr\u00ed ra sao n\u1eefa. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00ec b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-vi-hien-tai-va-tuong-lai-tottenham-hay-vo-dich-world-cup-421-190976.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/goc-nhin-vi-hien-tai-va-tuong-lai-tottenham-hay-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-vi-hien-tai-va-tuong-lai-tottenham-hay-vo-dich-world-cup-421-190976.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: V\u00ec hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, Tottenham h\u00e3y v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup!</span><br>\r\nTottenham ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 CLB \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao Spurs n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111ang hi\u1ec3n hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 n\u00e9t, \u00e2u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4534","checkdouble":"191867"},{"date":"01:26 24/07","title":"Mbappe x\u00fai gi\u1ee5c Kante b\u1ecf Chelsea sang PSG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/mbappe-xui-giuc-kante-bo-chelsea-sang-psg.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Kylian Mbappe ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch PSG nh\u1edd c\u1eady l\u00f4i k\u00e9o \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng N\u2019Golo Kante tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Ph\u00e1p trong su\u1ed1t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00f3ng g\u00f3p vai tr\u00f2 t\u1ed1i quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a N\u2019Golo Kante m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ph\u1ea3i th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a anh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd nghi\u00eam t\u00fac h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i gia Paris Saint-Germain, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nh\u01b0 theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Kylian Mbappe, m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 \u1ea2 R\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1edd c\u1eady anh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00f4i k\u00e9o \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u201cC\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed\u201d trong su\u1ed1t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe x\u00fai gi\u1ee5c Kante b\u1ecf Chelsea sang PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mbappe x\u00fai gi\u1ee5c Kante b\u1ecf Chelsea sang PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/mbappe-xui-giuc-kante-bo-chelsea-sang-psg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe x\u00fai gi\u1ee5c Kante b\u1ecf Chelsea sang PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng tu\u1ed5i teen ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn cho N\u2019Golo khi anh em g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf World Cup trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi anh \u1ea5y v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai hay chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng ra sao \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1ebf l\u00e0 t\u00f4i g\u1eedi qua m\u1ea9u m\u1ea5u gi\u1ea5y \u0111\u00fat t\u00fai N\u2019Golo, hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 \u0111em ra \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin nh\u1eafn t\u1eeb PSG. Anh \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u00f3i v\u1eady th\u00f4i ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 cu\u1ed7m Kante ra kh\u1ecfi Chelsea th\u00ec g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u1edf Stamford Bridge, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-421-191369.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-421-191369.html\">Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong> <o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4533","checkdouble":"191870"},{"date":"06:30 24/07","title":"Rooney c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o M.U v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec3m h\u1ecda kh\u00f4n l\u01b0\u1eddng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/6/rooney-canh-bao-mu-ve-hiem-hoa-khon-luong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo r\u1ea5t s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 trong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney khuy\u00ean M.U gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Martial, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ph\u1ea3i \u00f4m h\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMartial tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi M.U<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Old Trafford, tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y Martial \u0111ang b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m t\u00f9 b\u1edfi Jose Mourinho. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, v\u00e0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Martial c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u1ee1 su\u1ea5t l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 ng\u1ed3i nh\u00ecn \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Martial &ndash; \u00f4ng Philippe Lamboley th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: &ldquo;Sau khi xem x\u00e9t t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, v\u00e2ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man United.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y. M.U kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Anthony ra \u0111i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra trong 8 th\u00e1ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Anthony tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wayne Rooney khuy\u00ean MU gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Martial b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Wayne Rooney khuy\u00ean MU gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Martial b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Wayne-Rooney-khuyen-MU-giu-chan-Martial-bang-moi-gia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wayne Rooney khuy\u00ean M.U gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Martial m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, Wayne Rooney l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 \u0111ang ph\u1ea1m ph\u1ea3i sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f4n ngoan. Theo c\u00e1ch t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 CLB c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Anthony. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f4i khi r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Anthony. M\u1ed9t khi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef cho Anthony \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vui v\u1ebb, khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; Rooney khuy\u00ean M.U gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Martial.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, M.U ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Martial cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i Premier League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-ban-anthony-martial-neu-172-191841.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/mu-chi-ban-anthony-martial-neu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-ban-anthony-martial-neu-172-191841.html\">MU ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu...</span><br>\r\nMU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Manchester Evening News \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-khung-mu-172-191806.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/21/chelsea-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-khung-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-khung-mu-172-191806.html\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU thay Eden Hazard, theo t\u1edd The Times The Blues \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4532","checkdouble":"191873"},{"date":"06:43 24/07","title":"Sarri \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/sarri-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-cho-chelsea-he-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110ang b\u1ecb x\u00e2u x\u00e9 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, nh\u01b0ng t\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Maurizio Sarri t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSarri quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 Eden Hazard \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, trong khi Barca li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Willian. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Chelsea d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea &ndash; \u00f4ng Maurizio Sarri cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi, m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd qua \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i. Th\u1eadt vui khi c\u00f3 Courtois, Willian v\u00e0 Hazard trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u00f4i. V\u00ec v\u1eady, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sarri t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Sarri-tu-tin-giu-chan-tru-cot-o-mua-he-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y, khi h\u1ecd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Cobham \u0111\u1ec3 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp. Khi \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed v\u1ebd ra nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n, h\u1ecd mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, h\u1ecd b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng n\u0103m. C\u00f2n t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng b\u1ed9 ba n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u1edf Chelsea.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Willian r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Chelsea. V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i&rdquo; &ndash; Sarri t\u1ef1 tin tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Perth Glory, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng The Blues ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 12 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup. V\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sarri t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4n l\u01b0\u1eddng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, Chelsea s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Inter Milan \u1edf Nice v\u00e0 Arsenal t\u1ea1i Dublin trong gi\u1ea3i ICC, sau \u0111\u00f3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Man City trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh ng\u00e0y 5/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-perth-glory-01-chelsea-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-326-191854.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/video-tong-hop-perth-glory-01-chelsea-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-perth-glory-01-chelsea-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-326-191854.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Perth Glory 0-1 Chelsea (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)</span><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 59 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ebft l\u00fd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-chelsea-gian-nan-vi-thoi-duong-ho-di-hoa-172-191620.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/Sarri-tu-tin-giu-chan-tru-cot-o-mua-he-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-chelsea-gian-nan-vi-thoi-duong-ho-di-hoa-172-191620.html\">G\u00f3c Chelsea: Gian nan v\u00ec th\u00f3i &ldquo;d\u01b0\u1ee1ng h\u1ed5 di h\u1ecda&rdquo;</span><br>\r\n\u00cdt ng\u00e0y qua, HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh th\u1ebf n\u00e0o cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft Chelsea...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4531","checkdouble":"191875"},{"date":"06:56 24/07","title":"Sao Man City quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u1edbi HLV tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/24/sao-man-city-quyet-tam-chung-to-tai-nang-voi-hlv-tuyen-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf kh\u1ecfi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Leroy Sane quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSane mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf Joachim Low \u0111\u00e3 sai<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap Man City v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Leroy Sane b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 World Cup v\u00ec \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Joachim Low, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Man xanh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eddi tuy\u1ec3n, v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u1ea5y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u00f4i suy ngh\u0129. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leroy Sane quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c sau c\u00fa s\u1ed1c World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Leroy Sane quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c sau c\u00fa s\u1ed1c World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/sane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leroy Sane quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngu\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed7i \u0111au, nh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mong ch\u1edd nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ti\u1ebfp theo. T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu s\u00f3t, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n n\u1eefa&rdquo; - Leroy Sane quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, anh ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t: &ldquo;Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t HLV th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. Phong c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Napoli tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi CLB c\u1ee7a Sarri.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u00f3 th\u1ec3, Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sane-khong-trach-low-vi-quyet-dinh-o-nha-xem-world-cup-421-191790.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/sane-khong-trach-low-vi-quyet-dinh-o-nha-xem-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sane-khong-trach-low-vi-quyet-dinh-o-nha-xem-world-cup-421-191790.html\">Sane kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1ch Low v\u00ec quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf nh\u00e0 xem World Cup</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u00ea th\u1ea3m, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Leroy Sane kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1ch HLV Joachim...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cong-than-man-city-quyet-tam-dao-tau-khoi-ach-pep-guardiola-172-191855.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/cong-than-man-city-quyet-tam-dao-tau-khoi-ach-pep-guardiola.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cong-than-man-city-quyet-tam-dao-tau-khoi-ach-pep-guardiola-172-191855.html\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n Man City quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea9u kh\u1ecfi \u00e1ch Pep Guardiola</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Joe Hart tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 anh tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i, l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u00e3i m\u00e3i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p cho m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4530","checkdouble":"191876"},{"date":"14:56 23/07","title":"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Suarez khoe s\u1eafp c\u00f3 th\u00eam con","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/tien-dao-suarez-khoe-sap-co-them-con.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sofia Balbi cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u to ra nhanh ch\u00f3ng khi mang thai \u0111\u1ee9a con th\u1ee9 ba.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Gia \u0111\u00ecnh Suarez \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf bi\u1ec3n sau World Cup 2018. Uruguay b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft b\u1edfi Ph\u00e1p - \u0111\u1ed9i sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Barca khoe \u1ea3nh qu\u1ef3 g\u1ed1i, \u00f4m v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 h\u00f4n l\u00ean b\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a c\u00f4. H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a anh cho th\u1ea5y v\u00f2ng ba c\u1ee7a Sofia Balbi kh\u00e1 to. Tuy nhi\u00ean, gi\u1edbi t\u00ednh thai nhi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Suarez v\u00e0 Sofia Balbi c\u00f3 hai con m\u1ed9t trai m\u1ed9t g\u00e1i l\u00e0 Delfina v\u00e0 Benjamin.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/cc-6175-1532223158.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay g\u1eb7p Arab Saudi \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Suarez th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tin vui v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c v\u1ee3 mang b\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ee9a con th\u1ee9 ba. Sau khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf ph\u00fat 23, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch chia vui v\u1edbi c\u00e1c fan. Anh chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n: \"H\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Uruguay v\u1edbi 100 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Vui m\u1eebng h\u01a1n l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0a con th\u1ee9 ba c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1eafp ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n v\u00ec s\u1ef1 y\u00eau m\u1ebfn, \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi \u0111\u1ee9a con th\u1ee9 ba s\u1eafp ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Barca \"\u0111u\u1ed5i k\u1ecbp\" b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf CLB x\u1ee9 Catalonia l\u00e0 Messi - ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba \u0111\u00f3n qu\u00fd t\u1eed th\u1ee9 ba trong n\u0103m nay. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo b\u1eadn d\u1ef1 World Cup, Suarez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n \u1edf Barca, kh\u00f4ng tham gia c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Uruguay t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau Cup T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi Sevilla tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi La Liga kh\u1edfi tranh.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4529","checkdouble":"191835"},{"date":"15:17 23/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea mang c\u1ea3 Italia sang x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/tan-hlv-chelsea-mang-ca-italia-sang-xu-so-suong-mu.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4528","checkdouble":"191837"}]}